com.travelbank.knit.components

Class ModelManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.travelbank.knit.InternalModel
      • com.travelbank.knit.components.ModelManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MemoryEntity, ModelInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestModelManager

    public class ModelManager
extends InternalModel
    This component manages all models. It holds ComponentTags for all active models. All presenters have an instance if this. When they make requests to a model data, it goes through here . A model that generates the matching data is found then the EntityInstance of that presenter is passed on to receive results.
    See Also:
    InternalPresenter, InternalModel
